{"tid":1955564,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【本土研究社】【毋忘手足】數據證實政府濫捕濫告香港人再創高峰!","createTime":"2020-04-02T14:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T02:31:14.000Z","uid":138409,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3c6bca7480526ada790fdf8cc024ddf72a7bc397","tid":1955564,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T14:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BBhJd9p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBBhJd9p.png&h=b952b3f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/posts/2953167278112659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2Fposts%2F2953167278112659&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMt%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=100940e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/posts/2953167278112659</a><br />\n最新立法會財委會問題中提到的保安局數字，顯示自2019年因反修例運動被捕的人數高達7,613人，<span style=\"color: gold;\">遠超當年六七暴動過6,000人的紀錄</span>。<br />\n撇除極少數因咬破耳仔、連儂牆劏肚等罪行被拘捕的「藍絲暴徒」，以上數字即代表現時每1,000名香港人中，大概就有1個手足因近月社會運動而被拘捕。其餘721元朗恐襲涉事白衣人、煽惑暴力721「教人打仔」的經濟日報副社長石鏡泉、831集體濫用暴力的黑警卻繼續逃之夭夭。<br />\n律政署最新數字更能發現近4年來以《公安條例》的檢控失敗率，<span style=\"color: gold;\">由2016年53.1% 再升至2019年60.5% (直至9月)，成功檢控率不足四成。事實上，政府以《公安條例》將市民入罪本身門檻已經相當低，但仍然有過6成都被裁定罪名不成立</span>，印證了近年濫捕濫告的「復仇」行徑，已經成為香港打壓社會運動的手段的新常態。<br />\n無限濫用法律資源打壓公民社會，都是威權政府的共同特質，亦可預視未來復仇式濫告將會更加嚴重。希望各位更加關注及支援因反修例運動而被捕的手足真實處境，不要讓他們只成為濫捕濫告的一個數字。<br />\n--<br />\n參與資料<br />\n【註一】立法會財委會 (律政署) &mdash; 問題編號：1999<br />\n【註二】立法會財委會 (律政署) &mdash; 問題編號：0588<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr19-20/chinese/fc/fc/w_q/sj-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr19-20%2Fchinese%2Ffc%2Ffc%2Fw_q%2Fsj-c.pdf&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMt%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=778db523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr19-20/chinese/fc/fc/w_q/sj-c.pdf</a><br />\n--<br />\n 別讓官方數據隱沒真象 支持開放政府研究工作<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JKttLT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JKttLT&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMt%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=99f4e53b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JKttLT</a><br />\n記著Follow我地：<br />\n IG: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/liberresearch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fliberresearch%2F&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMt%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=611e0b17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/liberresearch/</a><br />\n TG: <a href=\"http://t.me/liberinfo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fliberinfo&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMt%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=60fa3f1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/liberinfo</a><br />\n Youtube: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2WOIKTk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WOIKTk&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMt%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=e5ec8a77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2WOIKTk</a>"},{"pid":"a03a630e0fbc6082dd5ec6d27cbcb3f6bfa24172","tid":1955564,"uid":291921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T14:22:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f249932da7aa6c7fcdef07a4313c93c2d35ea009","tid":1955564,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:06:42.000Z","msg":"大家都知&hellip;"},{"pid":"d20506481d28a1ac773aa3f4fb0bc9ab694440af","tid":1955564,"uid":43322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f249932da7aa6c7fcdef07a4313c93c2d35ea009","tid":1955564,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:06:42.000Z","msg":"大家都知&hellip;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:13:57.000Z","msg":"有好多人扮唔知 隊個數據出黎收佢皮係好事"},{"pid":"bb01e8ed27f1752e9039701285c41cc8399f82e1","tid":1955564,"uid":61197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:30:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59ab7bd45c973084e338804c52ab74b6500c70b2","tid":1955564,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":